divs: Sighting DetailsTalking on the telephone to my daughter in Wisconsin when I noticed a very unusual object in the sky. There were red and white lights and the shape was a large V. It was moving from the east to west at a slow rate of speed then picked up speed and left quickly. Never have seen anything like this and told my daughter while I was watching it. I was married to a retired USAF Major. I know planes and this was very odd. Not a planet, it was moving, it was low in the sky and quite large. Motion was steady until it increased in speed. I was calm and told my daughter about the event. Object should still be moving west over the country right now.
Summary: very large object, not an aircraft, moving over Paxton at 915PM.
